T02TD3456E:112a-1: dharma dh'a tu b'a g'i shva ra s'a dha nam ba shya bi dhi:/
T02TD3456E:112a-3: chos kyi dbyings ngag gi dbang phyug gis grub thabs dbang du bya ba'i cho ga /'phags pa 'jam dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3456E:112b-0: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas 'dir stong @112b pa nyid du bsgoms pa'i rjes la padma dang zla ba la gnas pa'i ho:yig dmar po yongs su gyur pa las phyag brgyad pa zhal bzhi pa /
T02TD3456E:112b-2: g-yas kyi gur gum ltar dmar ba /
T02TD3456E:112b-3: rgyab kyi padma r'a ga ltar dmar ba /
T02TD3456E:112b-5: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis kyis gzhu dang /
T02TD3456E:112b-7: phyi ma dag gis zhags pa dang /
T02TD3456E:112b-9: yang phyi ma dag gis shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i po ti dang /
T02TD3456E:112b-11: de bzhin du phyi ma dag gis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3456E:112b-12: chags pa chen pos sgeg pa'i nyams 'bar ba /
T02TD3456E:112b-13: sna tshogs padma dang zla ba la rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
T02TD3456E:112b-15: rgyan dang 'od pag tu med pa dang /
T02TD3456E:112b-16: ral pa'i cod pan gyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3456E:112b-17: snying ga'i sa bon gyi 'od zer gyis sems can rnams bkug nas rang dbang med pa'i gnas la bkod de sngags zlas par bya'o //
T02TD3456E:112b-18: aom ma h'a r'a ga badzra r'a ga ya sarba satva na ho /
T02TD3456E:112b-20: chos kyi dbyings ngag gi dbang phyug gi sgrub thabs kyis dbang du bya ba'i cho ga rdzogs so//
